---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import aboutMe from "./../assets/img/aboutme.jpg";
---

<div class="relative z-5 box-border w-9/12 m-auto pt-20 lg:my-20">
  <div
    class="flex flex-row items-center m-auto z-5 lg:flex-row md:flex-col sm:flex-col"
    id="about-me"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col w-8/12 mb-12 lg:mr-20">
      <Image
        src={aboutMe}
        alt="A bird sitting on a nest of eggs."
        class="w-full rounded-lg object-cover light:shadow-lg"
      />
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col z-5 mb-20">
      <div
        class="text-2xl text-myBlue leading-8 tracking-wide mb-4 md:text-2xl md:leading-8 md:tracking-tighter lg:text-4xl"
      >
        I'm Nico, a <u>software developer</u> currently working in redbee studios,
        taking client ideas to next level, using agile methodologies and good practices
        in Buenos Aires, Argentina. ðŸš€
      </div>
      <p
        class="text-xl tracking-tight text-gray-600 md:p-4 md:text-sm leading-5 lg:text-xl"
      >
        I've spent the past 7 years working across different areas of software
        development; making my career as a full stack developer. I love turning
        complex problems into elegant, user-friendly solutions.
      </p>
      <p
        class="text-xl tracking-tight text-gray-600 md:p-4 md:text-sm leading-5 lg:text-xl"
      >
        I believe in not just writing code, but in thinking deeply about the
        products I help to build, ensuring they're as enjoyable to use as they
        were for me to create. <br /><br />
        <button
          class="bg-myBlue text-white font-semibold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg shadow hover:bg-myBlue-dark transition ease-in-out duration-150"
        >
          Download CV
        </button>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .flex-row {
    display: flex;
    margin: auto;
    z-index: 5;
    align-items: center;
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      flex-direction: column;
      height: auto;
    }
  }
  .title {
    font-size: 35px;
    line-height: 50px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      padding: 1rem;
      font-size: 20px;
      line-height: 20px;
      letter-spacing: 0px;
    }
  }
  .text {
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 34px;
    letter-spacing: 0px;
    color: gray;
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      padding: 1rem;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 20px;
      letter-spacing: 0px;
    }
  }
</style>
